('20201027004', '계약 품목유형 변경 요청', '<p>RFQ건에 대해(1건은 계약완료됨) <strong>품목유형을 일반용역에서 외주용역으로 변경 </strong>부탁드립니다.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>외주정비단가계약건에 대해서는 내부적으로 외주용역으로 통일하자고 했는데 제가 일반용역으로 만들었습니다.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>내역 확인 후 변경 부탁드립니다.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>※ 상세내역</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:321px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black; border-image:none; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; height:22px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap; width:79px\">RFQ</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:windowtext windowtext windowtext black; border-image:none; border-style:solid solid solid none; border-width:1px 1px 1px medium; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap; width:243px\">건명</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black windowtext windowtext; border-image:none; border-style:none solid solid; border-width:medium 1px 1px; height:22px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap\">8122</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black windowtext windowtext black; border-image:none; border-style:none solid solid none; border-width:medium 1px 1px medium; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap\">집진기 정비</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black windowtext windowtext; border-image:none; border-style:none solid solid; border-width:medium 1px 1px; height:22px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap\">8121</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black windowtext windowtext black; border-image:none; border-style:none solid solid none; border-width:medium 1px 1px medium; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap\">펌프 정비</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-color:black windowtext windowtext; border-image:none; border-style:none solid solid; border-width:medium 1px 1px; height:22px; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap\">8120<