('20210524015', '근무스케줄 탄력근로 오픈', '<p>근무스케줄관리시스템 - 유연근로 - 탄력근로신청<br />\r\n&nbsp;- 탄력근로 오픈</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\ndefault-layouts.jsp<br />\r\nspringWorking.jsp<br />\r\nspringWorkingAppr.jsp</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AgreementController.java<br />\r\nSelectWorkingController.java<br />\r\nSpringWorkingController.java</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AgreementMapper.java<br />\r\nAgreementService.java<br />\r\nAgreementServiceImpl.java</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PlanMapper.java<br />\r\nPlanServiceImpl.java<br />\r\nSelectPlanService.java</p>\r\n\r\n<p>agreement-mapper.xml<br />\r\nplan-mapper.xml</p>\r\n', 'S00', 'S01', 'WT01', 'ST10', '노무행정섹션', '강한', '현희문', '2021-04-01', '2021-05-04', '2021-05-04', 30, 0, 14, NULL, '2021-05-24', '2021-05-24'),
